channel.title: VPS error connecting to server HELP(VPSLand.com)
channel.description:
ok my server is online and the server status checker can check my server status (so ip is changed at no-ip)
but when i try to logg in my server i get the error: can't connect to server. when i check my VPS and check the connections it shows only the status checker and not any other connections....(so no one can connect)
in my Client's GUI is the ip changed to the one of the VPS (no-ip one) but still. can't connect
